short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically admit join requests from external guests to Google Meet

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically click the "Admit" button when a join request comes in from external guests. Please disable the extension in chrome://extensions when you want to disable the behavior.
